      <title>巴西的糖领导人Raizen出售资产，削减投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/brazil-s-top-sugar-maker-raizen-to-sell-assets-trim-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西最大的糖和乙醇制造商Raizen SA正在寻找潜在的资产销售，并停止建造新工厂，以减少借贷成本在该国飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/brazil-s-top-sugar-maker-raizen-to-sell-assets-trim-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Feb 2025 15:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中国技术的提升，新兴股票上升到三个月高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/emerging-stocks-rise-to-three-month-high-as-deepseek-lifts-mood</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在腾讯控股有限公司（Tencent Holdings Ltd.）搬迁以整合DeepSeek的AI模式，并以北京表示对私营部门的认可，这是恢复经济增长的关键，因此新兴市场股票攀升至三个月高，在中国改善的情绪中提高了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/emerging-stocks-rise-to-three-month-high-as-deepseek-lifts-mood</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Feb 2025 04:12:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
